				"delay": "1.040", "time": "12.433", "mood": "L5", "value": "AA: That could mean anything! Could it be a memory I remember the most vividly? Or similarly a memory that changed who I am for the better? I simply could not know, so I changed the question to suit myself."
			}
		],
