			{
				"delay": "1.220", "time": "31.625", "mood": "L1", "value": "AA: This answer I do not \"think\" at all Michael. I know this answer. On a particularly cold evening I decided to allow myself the privilege of egressing this wretched place, unbeknownst to my aunt, and retreated to the relative safety of... the home of my other friend at the time. We watched my favourite show, Madoka Magica, and shared stories and I daresay it made us two girls feel magical. That is my answer."
			}
		],
